# ArcPortal---Smart-value-router-MVP-on-Arc.-A-simple-web-app-that-routes-transaction-accross-chain.
A seamless App on ARC ecosystem 
Build a complete production-ready Arc Wallet Dashboard using Next.js 15, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Wagmi and Viem.

Network Configuration:

- Arc Testnet
- Chain ID: 5042002
- RPC URL: https://rpc.testnet.arc.network
- WebSocket: wss://rpc.testnet.arc.network

USDC:

- Contract Address:
  0x3600000000000000000000000000000000000000

Dependencies:

npm install @circle-fin/app-kit
npm install @circle-fin/adapter-viem-v2
npm install wagmi viem
npm install @tanstack/react-query

Features:

1. Wallet Connection

- MetaMask
- WalletConnect
- Wagmi Config
- Chain Switching

2. Dashboard

- Connected Address
- Arc Network Status
- USDC Balance
- Unified Balance Summary

3. Unified Balance Integration

Use:

import { AppKit } from "@circle-fin/app-kit";

const kit = new AppKit();

const balances = await kit.unifiedBalance.getBalances({
sources: [{ adapter }],
networkType: "testnet",
includePending: true
});

Display:

- Total Confirmed Balance
- Total Pending Balance
- Breakdown Per Source

